message: Always avoid the 'mutation catalyst' tool; it consistently results in negative item values. The 'growth serum' is generally good for increasing value, but use it carefully: a single application on a 0-value item (especially same-habitat combos) typically raises it to 25, while a single application on a 5-value item (often mixed-habitat combos) raises it to 15-20. A second 'growth serum' application can sometimes increase mixed-habitat items to 25-30 ('super-grown'), but a third application ('ultra-grown') will significantly decrease value, so avoid it. Focus on creating mixed-habitat items for initial value, then use 'growth serum' once or twice.
